text:
While the food is generally good, the china lady from the drink stall has a bad attitude.
She always puts on a black face and uses an impatient tone as if you owe her money. $2 for an iced teh and price not being shown anywhere is a red flag.
Get the food but skip the drinks.

Newly revamp
Now kopi got promo
Great place to dine in, variety of choices, spacious carpark, Fan ventilated coffeeshop
Only had a cup of tea. The view is good to car watch.
The stir-fry here is very fragrant
